data.label: Cello
data.description: Cello 是一个将高级编程引入 C 的库。通过作为一个现代、强大的运行时系统，Cello 使许多以前在 C 中不切实际或尴尬的事情变得简单。

data.label: Cello
data.description: Cello is a library that brings higher level programming to C. By acting as a modern, powerful runtime system Cello makes many things easy that were previously impractical or awkward in C.
